Once upon a time there lived a crocodile and his wife. There also lived a monkey on a tree.The crocodile and monkey were friends.
One day the crocodile's wife asked her husband to eat the heart of the monkey. The crocodile went to the monkey and told him 
that today he is orgnising a feast at his home and he came here to invite the monkey for it. the crocodile took
the monkey with him and told him that his wife wants to eat his heart that's why he is taking the monkey with him.
when the monkey heard it, he told the crocodile that he has not brought his heart along with him andforgot it at
his home. he told the crocodile to take him back to his home so that he can take his heart with him .